Stefano_package.components._2d

Class CadCircle

  • java.lang.Object
    • Stefano_package.components.CadComponent
      • Stefano_package.components._2d.CadCircle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICadComponent

    public class CadCircle
extends CadComponent
    This concrete class represent a circle, with the base point being the center. It has a static number that helps generating automatically non-colliding names and obviously center and radius parameters.
